	UCNA-PENELOPE2011
        Robert W. Pattie Jr.
	Nov 22,2012

        This repository contains the source code for a simulation of the UCNA experiment using the PENELOPE 2011 
        Monte Carlo package.  The source code for PENELOPE is not included sinc it is a control problem and I 
        sign a form saying I wouldn't distribute it.  So get it from Oak Ridge National Lab.  Once that is done
        link and compile the code found here with the penelope.f, pengeom.f, penvared.f, timer.f oh just look in 
        the Makefile.
       
